What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#Roblox #foltyn

snippet.title: Wuyang | New Hero Gameplay Trailer | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
Wuyang is finally here for some hydration domination!

As a prodigy from Wuxing University’s Water College, Wuyang redefines what it means to heal with a hybrid playstyle built on flow, precision, and constant disruption.

With his Xuanwu Staff and mobility-focused kit, you’ll be able to support or deal pressure depending on the situation, and reposition yourself with ease to escape danger or claim space. 

Make a splash as Wuyang during his limited-time trial Aug 14–18 and keep the party going when he officially arrives in Season 18.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC

_

snippet.description:
It's the Honest Trailer for K-Pop Demon Hunters! The movie that answers "what if Blackpink were all moonlighting as Buffy the Vampire Slayer?” It’s a story about friendship, saving the world, and never getting to 1st base with your crush because he's about 375 years older than you. Songs are super catchy though and the animation looks great. Do we like K-Pop now? I think we like K-Pop now!

Comment below with the movie you’d like to see us take on next!

snippet.title: In Whose Name? | Teaser Trailer | Only In Theaters September 19
snippet.description:
Then eighteen-year-old Nicolas Ballesteros is thrust into the eye of the storm that is Ye, a man building empires in music, fashion, and faith. Coming to terms with Bipolar, his collapsing marriage, vanishing sponsorships, and growing public backlash, Ye’s life unfolds alongside a billion-dollar brand and a persona as polarizing as it is powerful.

For six transformative years of 15-hour shoot days, Ballesteros did more than document a cultural icon. What began as a silent observation evolved into a profound journey of artistic and personal growth. Immersed in Ye’s world of extremes, he bore witness to brilliance and breakdowns, triumphs and turmoil, but also observed the paranoia and intensity that increasingly shaped Ye’s world.

In the end, Ballesteros captured not just a portrait of Ye but a reflection of the human condition in all its contradictions. The camera never blinks as Ye speaks candidly about living with bipolar disorder, offering rare insight into the realities of mental illness and its impact on identity, perception, and power. Through a personal lens, the film considers how mental health is handled - or left unspoken - among the weight of visibility and vulnerability.
Ye returns to his childhood home in Chicago, walking through its empty rooms with neighbors who knew his family when he was a boy. In these moments, stripped of fame, he reflects on his roots, his grief, and the family he longs to hold onto. Walking through Ye’s inner circle, we see the loyal, the opportunistic, and the legendary; a man alternately driven by vision and consumed by ambition.

In Whose Name? invites viewers to sit with contradiction, to witness a modern myth in motion, and draw their own conclusions. The film reveals a side of Ye the world was never meant to see - raw, unfiltered, and suspended in the complexity of fame, faith, mental health, and power. The result is a story carved from 3,000 hours of raw footage, a collision of turmoil and truth, and an unflinching chronicle of ambition, collapse, and the long road to redemption.

In Whose Name? invites viewers to sit with contradiction, to witness a modern myth in motion, and draw their own conclusions. The film reveals a side of Ye the world was never meant to see - raw, unfiltered, and suspended in the complexity of fame, faith, mental health, and power. The result is a story carved from 3,000 hours of raw footage, a collision of turmoil and truth, and an unflinching chronicle of ambition, collapse, and the long road to redemption.

snippet.title: Alien: Earth - Official "Homage" Trailer (2025)
snippet.description:
The original trailer for Ridley Scott's film Alien has been recreated using footage from Noah Hawley's new show, Alien: Earth.

When a mysterious space vessel crash-lands on Earth, a young woman and a ragtag group of tactical soldiers make a fateful discovery that puts them face-to-face with the planet’s greatest threat in the sci-fi horror series “Alien: Earth.” As members of the crash recovery crew search for survivors among the wreckage, they encounter mysterious predatory life forms more terrifying than they could have ever imagined. With this new threat unlocked, the search crew must fight for survival and what they choose to do with this discovery could change planet Earth as they know it.
 
Lead by Sydney Chandler, the series showcases an expansive international cast which includes Alex Lawther, Timothy Olyphant, Essie Davis, Samuel Blenkin, Babou Ceesay, David Rysdahl, Adrian Edmondson, Adarsh Gourav, Jonathan Ajayi, Erana James, Lily Newmark, Diem Camille and Moe Bar-El.

FX’s Alien: Earth premieres August 12th on FX | Hulu.

#IGN

アベンジャーズ/ドゥームズデイ/デッドプールのティーザー、ライアン・レイノルズ監督の次回作デッドプール、X-フォース関連映画、アベンジャーズ/ドゥームズデイ、シークレット・ウォーズの計画についてご紹介します。デッドプール4の発表。ライアン・レイノルズがマーベルにおけるデッドプールの映画とテレビ番組の将来について説明。アベンジャーズ/6/シークレット・ウォーズ/X-MENの計画について解説。マーベル・ミュータント・サーガ フェイズ7、X-MEN新作映画。

マーベルがMCUをリブートする理由、そして『アベンジャーズ／シックス・シークレット・ウォーズ』でマーベル映画とディズニープラスのマーベルTV番組を全てリブートする理由。そして、アベンジャーズ、ニューアイアンマン、ウルヴァリン、デッドプール、ファンタスティック・フォー、ゴーストライダー、スパイダーマンといったX-MENミュータントたち、そして以前の映画では思い通りに使えなかった他のマーベルキャラクターたちに何が変わるのか。

マーベルのリブートと、ディズニープラスで配信予定の映画とマーベルTV番組への変更点。マーベルMCUリブート計画の詳細。マーベルに何が起こったのか、ディズニープラスのストリーミング問題、そしてマーベルの修復

एवेंजर्स डूम्सडे डेडपूल टीज़र, रयान रेनॉल्ड्स का अगला डेडपूल प्रोजेक्ट, एक्स-फोर्स फ़िल्में, एवेंजर्स डूम्सडे, सीक्रेट वॉर्स की योजनाएँ। डेडपूल 4 की घोषणा। रयान रेनॉल्ड्स मार्वल में डेडपूल फ़िल्मों और टीवी शोज़ के भविष्य के बारे में बताते हैं। एवेंजर्स 6 सीक्रेट वॉर्स एक्स-मेन की योजना की व्याख्या। मार्वल फ़ेज़ 7 म्यूटेंट सागा, नई एक्स-मेन फ़िल्में।

डेडपूल और वूल्वरिन के लिए रयान रेनॉल्ड्स पर मुकदमा क्यों? मार्वल चुटकुले, हटाए गए दृश्य, रयान रेनॉल्ड्स और ब्लेक लाइवली का मुकदमा। इसके परिणामस्वरूप क्या होगा? और रयान रेनॉल्ड्स को चिंता करने की ज़रूरत क्यों नहीं है? और कैसे मार्वल, डेडपूल और वूल्वरिन इस मुकदमे का हिस्सा बन गए।

एक्स-23, वूल्वरिन बनाम हल्क, गैम्बिट हटाए गए दृश्य, ब्लेड हटाए गए दृश्य, सेबरटूथ, वूल्वरिन बनाम सेबरटूथ। डेडपूल बनाम डिज़्नी चुटकुले, केविन फीगे मार्वल चुटकुले और चौथी दीवार का टूटना। डेडपूल और वूल्वरिन के पोस्ट क्रेडिट सीन चुटकुले। दुष्ट आयरन मैन दृश्य, द पनिशर कैमियो दृश्य, एक्स-मेन दृश्य, डेडपूल के और रूप, वूल्वरिन के और रूप। एडमेंटियम की व्याख्या। बेन एफ्लेक डेयरडेविल रेफरेंस, इलेक्ट्रा, डेडपूल ने वूल्वरिन को क्यों बचाया, द एक्स-मेन, फैंटास्टिक फोर और डेडपूल ने MCU को कैसे बचाया। डेडपूल और वूल्वरिन ने बैटलवर्ल्ड और लोकी सीज़न 2 के साथ एवेंजर्स 6 सीक्रेट वॉर्स की शुरुआत कैसे की, जिसका अंत गॉड लोकी क्रॉसओवर ईस्टर एग्स के साथ हुआ।

मार्वल MCU को रीबूट क्यों कर रहा है, सभी मार्वल फ़िल्में और डिज़्नी प्लस मार्वल टीवी शोज़ एवेंजर्स 6 सीक्रेट वॉर्स के साथ। और सभी एवेंजर्स, न्यू आयरन मैन, एक्स-मेन म्यूटेंट जैसे वूल्वरिन, डेडपूल, फैंटास्टिक फोर, घोस्ट राइडर, स्पाइडर-मैन और अन्य किरदारों के साथ क्या बदलने वाला है, जिन्हें मार्वल पिछली फ़िल्मों में अपनी इच्छानुसार इस्तेमाल नहीं कर पाया था।

मार्वल रीबूट और डिज़्नी प्लस पर आने वाली फ़िल्मों और मार्वल टीवी शोज़ में वे क्या बदलाव कर रहे हैं। मार्वल MCU रीबूट योजनाओं की व्याख्या। मार्वल का क्या हुआ, डिज़्नी प्लस स्ट्रीमिंग की समस्याएँ, और मार्वल का समाधान

जल्द ही और भी कई मार्वल ट्रेलर आएंगे: एवेंजर्स 5 डूम्सडे ट्रेलर, थंडरबोल्ट्स ट्रेलर, एवेंजर्स 6 सीक्रेट वॉर्स ट्रेलर और स्पाइडर-मैन ब्रैंड न्यू डे ट्रेलर वीडियो!

라이언 레이놀즈가 데드풀과 울버린 때문에 소송을 당한 이유. 마블 농담, 삭제 장면, 라이언 레이놀즈와 블레이크 라이블리 소송. 그 결과 어떤 일이 벌어질까요? 그리고 라이언 레이놀즈가 걱정할 필요가 없는 이유. 그리고 마블, 데드풀, 울버린이 어떻게 소송에 휘말리게 되었을까요?

X-23, 울버린 대 헐크, 갬빗 삭제 장면, 블레이드 삭제 장면, 세이버투스, 울버린 대 세이버투스. 데드풀 대 디즈니 농담, 케빈 파이기 마블 농담, 그리고 제4의 벽 붕괴. 데드풀과 울버린 포스트 크레딧 장면 농담. 사악한 아이언맨 장면, 퍼니셔 카메오 장면, 엑스맨 장면, 더 많은 데드풀 변형, 더 많은 울버린 변형. 아다만티움에 대한 설명. 벤 애플렉의 데어데블 관련 언급, 일렉트라, 데드풀이 울버린을 구하는 이유, 엑스맨, 판타스틱 포, 그리고 데드풀이 MCU를 구하는 이유. 데드풀과 울버린이 어벤져스 6 시크릿 워즈를 배틀월드로 설정하고, 로키 시즌 2를 갓 로키 크로스오버 이스터 에그로 마무리하는 방식

마블이 어벤져스 6 시크릿 워즈로 MCU를 리부트하는 이유, 모든 마블 영화와 디즈니 플러스 마블 TV 시리즈. 어벤져스, 뉴 아이언맨, 엑스맨, 울버린 같은 뮤턴트, 데드풀, 판타스틱 포, 고스트 라이더, 스파이더맨 등 마블의 기존 캐릭터들이 이전 영화에서 원하는 방식으로 활용하지 못했던 모든 캐릭터들이 어떻게 변할 것인지에 대한 이야기입니다.

마블 리부트와 디즈니 플러스에서 공개될 예정인 영화 및 마블 TV 프로그램에 대한 변화. 마블 MCU 리부트 계획 설명. 마블에 무슨 일이 일어났는지, 디즈니 플러스 스트리밍 문제, 그리고 마블의 개선 사항

곧 더 많은 마블 예고편이 공개됩니다! 어벤져스 5 둠즈데이 예고편, 썬더볼츠 예고편, 어벤져스 6 시크릿 워즈 예고편, 스파이더맨 브랜드 뉴 데이 예고편 영상!

snippet.title: AKA CHARLIE SHEEN | Official Trailer (2025)
snippet.description:
Tabloid black hole Charlie Sheen knows what’s been said about him, and he’s finally ready to confess. Directed by Andrew Renzi (Pepsi, Where’s My Jet?), aka Charlie Sheen tracks his upbringing in Malibu to his effortless rise to megastardom — and dramatic fall, all within the public eye. With a stunning clarity earned through seven years of sobriety, Sheen openly speaks about the subjects and events he's never discussed publicly before. Through extraordinarily candid interviews with his family, friends, and cast members, including Denise Richards, Heidi Fleiss, Jon Cryer, Sean Penn, Ramon Estevez, Brooke Mueller, Chris Tucker, and his drug dealer Marco, the most outrageous moments of Sheen’s life are revisited with raw emotion and exceptional warmth, painting a portrait of a flawed man whose penchant for self-destruction is ultimately no match for the ferocious love and forgiveness he inspires in those closest to him.

#charliesheen #documentary #netflix

snippet.title: Starting Over as NOOB with Secret Dragon Cannelloni in Steal a Brainrot!
snippet.description:
Starting Over as NOOB with Secret Dragon Cannelloni in Steal a Brainrot!

Socials:
Profile: https://www.roblox.com/users/8607372228/profile
Community: https://www.roblox.com/share/g/36097648

--

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#Roblox

You got it, girl, you got it (Oh, ooh, ayy)

Don't let them niggas try you, test your patience

All you need is me playin' on your playlist
You ain't gotta be frustrated


[Pre-Chorus: Chris Brown]
I don't wanna play no games, play no games (Oh)

(I don't wanna, I don't wanna)
Seen it on the 'Gram, I'm tryna see that shit in 3D, mami
I know I get around 'cause I like to move freely
(I don't, I don't)
But you could lock it down, I could tell by how you treat me
(I don't, I don't)

Good to have me on your side, I ain't sayin' that you need me (Yeah-yeah)
Six God talk but I ain't tryna get preachy (No, no-no)
I seen how you did homeboy, please take it easier on me
'Cause I don't wanna (No) play no games, play no games
(I don't wanna, I don't wanna)
I don't wanna play no games, play no games
(I don't, I don't)

I don't, I don't
No

Pre-order NHL 26 for 7 Day Early Access: https://x.ea.com/85081

Get a deeper look at ICE-Q 2.0, which utilizes powerful NHL EDGE data so you can think, move, and play like your favorite superstars. By informing player Attributes, Tendencies, and with the all-new Goalie Crease Control System, NHL EDGE data brings a deeper level of authenticity to Chel. ICE-Q 2.0 changes the way lines are constructed, along with players’ tactics from game to game and shift to shift.

X-Factors is taken to another level in NHL 26, enhancing an arsenal of 28 abilities in five different categories with unique animations, tactical gameplay outcomes, and tiers of impact. snippet.title: Playing RIDICULOUS Looking Slot Machines!
snippet.description:
We are BACK at the Casino playing all of the WEIRDEST Slot Machines we can find.  You know those ones that are 30 feet tall and no one ever seems to play... let's see if they can pay out!  Thank you all so much for liking, subscribing, and dropping your thoughts in the comments. Even if you’re roasting me—I still love you. You’re all beautiful, and I truly appreciate every single one of you for riding along on this crazy journey.  Wish me luck, and I’ll see you in the next one! Let’s go to war.

Brettski strolled into the casino with $5,000 in cash and a mischievous glint in his eye. He wasn’t here for the classics—no Buffalo, no Lightning Link. Tonight, he was hunting the strangest, tallest, most absurd slot machines the casino had to offer.

The first beast loomed over him like a mechanical skyscraper—30 feet tall, with a giant spinning wheel the size of a car tire. $25 a spin. Brettski hit the button and watched the wheel climb higher and higher until it landed on “Mega Bonus.” Sirens blared, lights exploded, and a crane inside the machine lowered a miniature treasure chest into view—$1,500 win right out of the gate.

Next was a bizarre slot shaped like a dragon’s head, its eyes glowing red. $50 a spin. The dragon roared with every press, breathing digital fire across the reels. Two spins later, Brettski triggered a bonus where he had to fight the dragon on-screen by choosing attacks. He slayed it, bagging another $2,200.

Then came the jellyfish machine—a neon, underwater monstrosity that pulsed like it was alive. It ate $800 in minutes. The next machine looked like a haunted grandfather clock; with each spin, the pendulum swung harder. It paid nothing, but Brettski couldn’t look away from its eerie ticking.

Finally, tucked in the back, Brettski found The Tower. A 30-foot alien mothership slot with holographic tentacles reaching toward the ceiling. $100 a spin. The first spin—nothing. Second—partial bonus. Third spin—three alien symbols lined up. The machine shook violently, lights flashing as if the casino itself was under attack.

Suddenly, the screen went black, replaced by text: “FINAL LEVEL UNLOCKED — PHYSICAL ACCESS REQUIRED.”

From somewhere above, the machine hissed. A hidden door in its base creaked open, revealing a narrow, dimly lit staircase… leading straight up inside the slot.

#slots #blackjack #gambling #casino #baccarat #roulette

Who is Brettski? Brettski is a Professional Gambler, similar to the ancient legends Vegas Matt, Bluff, DegenDalt, Mr. Hand Pay, or Lady Luck HQ! However, unlike these legends, Brettski has thousands of years of stored ancient knowledge harvested by the elders, at skills such as Slot Machines, Roulette, Blackjack, Craps, Bubble Craps, Poker, and Baccarat.  Brettski's goal as a Professional Gambler is simple: own all of Las Vegas, using funds made by Gambling.  Subscribe to support his journey in world domination.

ja.title: ばかばかしい見た目のスロットマシンをプレイ！
ja.description:
カジノに戻ってきました。見つけたら全部、とびきり奇妙なスロットマシンで遊んでいます。高さ30フィートもあるのに、誰も遊んでいないあのマシン… 果たしてペイアウトが出るのか、試してみましょう！ いいね！登録、チャンネル登録、そしてコメント欄へのご意見、本当にありがとうございます。たとえ私を批判していたとしても、私は皆さんのことが大好きです。皆さんは皆素晴らしいです。このクレイジーな旅に付き合ってくれた一人一人に、心から感謝しています。幸運を祈ってください。次回もお会いしましょう！さあ、戦いましょう。

ブレツキーは5,000ドルの現金と、いたずらっぽい目をした目でカジノに足を踏み入れました。彼は定番のスロットマシンを求めて来たわけではありません。バッファローもライトニングリンクもありません。今夜彼は、カジノで一番奇妙で、一番高くて、一番馬鹿げたスロットマシンを探し求めていたのです。

最初のモンスターは、まるで機械仕掛けの超高層ビルのように彼の前にそびえ立った。高さ30フィート、車のタイヤほどもある巨大な回転ホイール。1スピン25ドル。ブレツキーはボタンを押し、ホイールがどんどん高く上がっていき、「メガボーナス」に止まるのを見守った。サイレンが鳴り響き、ライトが爆発し、マシン内のクレーンが小さな宝箱を下ろした。まさに1,500ドルの勝利だ。

次は、ドラゴンの頭の形をした奇妙なスロット。目は赤く光っていた。1スピン50ドル。ドラゴンは押すたびに咆哮し、リール全体にデジタルの炎を吐き出した。2スピン後、ブレツキーはボーナスを発動させ、画面上のドラゴンと攻撃方法を選択して戦わなければならなかった。彼はドラゴンを倒し、さらに2,200ドルを手に入れた。

そしてクラゲマシンが登場した。ネオンカラーの水中モンスターは、まるで生きているかのように脈動していた。数分で800ドルを食い尽くした。次のマシンは、まるで幽霊の出るおじいさん時計のようだった。回すごとに振り子が激しく揺れていた。配当はゼロだったが、ブレツキーはその不気味な時を刻む音から目を離すことができなかった。

ついにブレツキーは奥まった場所に「ザ・タワー」を見つけた。天井に向かって伸びるホログラムの触手を持つ、高さ30フィート（約9メートル）のエイリアン母船スロット。1スピン100ドル。最初のスピンは何もなし。2回目は部分ボーナス。3回目はエイリアンのシンボルが3つ並んだ。マシンは激しく揺れ、カジノ自体が攻撃を受けているかのようにライトが点滅した。

突然、画面が真っ暗になり、「最終レベル解除 ― 物理的アクセスが必要です」という文字が浮かび上がった。

どこか上の方から、マシンがシューという音を立てた。台座の隠し扉がきしむ音を立てて開き、狭く薄暗い階段が現れた…スロットの中へとまっすぐ上へと続いていた。

#スロット #ブラックジャック #ギャンブル #カジノ #バカラ #ルーレット

Brettskiとは？Brettskiはプロのギャンブラーで、Vegas Matt、Bluff、DegenDalt、Mr. Hand Pay、Lady Luck HQといった伝説の人物と肩を並べる存在です。しかし、これらの伝説の人物とは異なり、Brettskiはスロットマシン、ルーレット、ブラックジャック、クラップス、バブルクラップス、ポーカー、バカラといったゲームにおいて、長老たちから受け継いだ数千年にわたる古代の知識を蓄積しています。Brettskiのプロギャンブラーとしての目標はシンプルです。ギャンブルで稼いだ資金を使って、ラスベガスを制覇することです。彼の世界制覇への旅を応援するために、ぜひチャンネル登録をお願いします。

fr-FR.title: Jouer à des machines à sous à l'aspect RIDICULE !
fr-FR.description:
Nous sommes de RETOUR au casino, à jouer à toutes les machines à sous les plus étranges que nous ayons pu trouver. Vous savez, celles qui font 9 mètres de haut et auxquelles personne ne semble jamais jouer… voyons si elles peuvent payer ! Merci à tous d'avoir aimé, de vous être abonnés et d'avoir laissé vos avis dans les commentaires. Même si vous me critiquez, je vous aime quand même. Vous êtes tous magnifiques, et j'apprécie sincèrement chacun d'entre vous de m'avoir accompagné dans cette folle aventure. Souhaitez-moi bonne chance, et à la prochaine ! En avant la guerre !

Brettski est entré au casino avec 5 000 $ en liquide et une lueur malicieuse dans le regard. Il n'était pas là pour les classiques – pas de Buffalo, pas de Lightning Link. Ce soir, il chassait les machines à sous les plus étranges, les plus hautes et les plus absurdes que le casino avait à offrir.

La première bête le dominait tel un gratte-ciel mécanique – 9 mètres de haut, avec une roue géante de la taille d'un pneu de voiture. 25 $ le tour. Brettski appuya sur le bouton et regarda la roue monter de plus en plus haut jusqu'à ce qu'elle s'arrête sur « Méga Bonus ». Les sirènes hurlèrent, les lumières explosèrent et une grue à l'intérieur de la machine fit descendre un coffre au trésor miniature : 1 500 $ de gains dès le départ.

Suivant, une étrange machine à sous en forme de tête de dragon, les yeux rouges. 50 $ par tour. Le dragon rugissait à chaque pression, crachant des flammes numériques sur les rouleaux. Deux tours plus tard, Brettski déclencha un bonus où il devait combattre le dragon à l'écran en choisissant des attaques. Il le tua, empochant 2 200 $ supplémentaires.

Puis arriva la machine à méduses : une monstruosité sous-marine lumineuse qui pulsait comme si elle était vivante. Elle engloutit 800 $ en quelques minutes. La machine suivante ressemblait à une horloge de parquet hantée ; à chaque tour, le pendule oscillait plus fort. Elle ne rapportait rien, mais Brettski ne pouvait détourner le regard de son étrange tic-tac.

Finalement, caché au fond, Brettski trouva la Tour. Une machine à sous extraterrestre de 9 mètres de haut, avec des tentacules holographiques s'élevant vers le plafond. 100 $ par tour. Premier tour : rien. Deuxième : bonus partiel. Troisième tour : trois symboles extraterrestres alignés. La machine trembla violemment, les lumières clignotant comme si le casino lui-même était attaqué.

Soudain, l'écran devint noir, remplacé par le texte : « DERNIER NIVEAU DÉBLOQUÉ – ACCÈS PHYSIQUE REQUIS. »

De quelque part au-dessus, la machine siffla. Une porte cachée à sa base s'ouvrit en grinçant, révélant un escalier étroit et faiblement éclairé… menant directement à l'intérieur de la machine à sous.

#machines à sous #blackjack #jeux d'argent #casino #baccarat #roulette

Qui est Brettski ? Brettski est un joueur professionnel, à l'instar des légendes anciennes Vegas Matt, Bluff, DegenDalt, Mr. Hand Pay ou Lady Luck HQ ! Cependant, contrairement à ces légendes, Brettski possède des milliers d'années de connaissances ancestrales, acquises par ses aînés, dans des domaines tels que les machines à sous, la roulette, le blackjack, le craps, le bubble craps, le poker et le baccarat. L'objectif de Brettski en tant que joueur professionnel est simple : conquérir tout Las Vegas grâce aux fonds gagnés grâce aux jeux d'argent. Abonnez-vous pour soutenir son aventure vers la domination du monde.

ko.title: 우스꽝스럽게 생긴 슬롯머신을 플레이해보세요!
ko.description:
카지노로 돌아와서 찾을 수 있는 온갖 기괴한 슬롯머신들을 돌려보고 있어요. 키가 30피트(약 9미터)나 되는데 아무도 안 하는 것 같은 슬롯머신 말이에요... 과연 당첨될지 한번 볼까요! 좋아요와 구독, 그리고 댓글로 여러분의 생각을 남겨주셔서 정말 감사합니다. 저를 욕하시더라도, 저는 여전히 여러분을 사랑해요. 모두 아름다우시고, 이 미친 여정에 함께해 주신 모든 분들께 진심으로 감사드립니다. 행운을 빌어주시고, 다음 슬롯에서 만나요! 자, 전쟁터로 가 볼까요?

브렛스키는 현금 5천 달러와 장난기 어린 눈빛을 지니며 카지노로 들어섰습니다. 그는 클래식 게임을 하러 온 게 아니었어요. 버팔로도, 라이트닝 링크도 없었죠. 오늘 밤, 그는 카지노에서 가장 기괴하고, 가장 높고, 가장 황당한 슬롯머신을 찾아다녔습니다.

첫 번째 괴물은 마치 기계로 만든 마천루처럼 그의 머리 위로 우뚝 솟아 있었다. 30피트 높이에 자동차 타이어만 한 거대한 바퀴가 돌아가고 있었다. 한 바퀴 돌리면 25달러. 브렛스키는 버튼을 누르고 바퀴가 점점 더 높이 올라가는 것을 지켜보았다. "메가 보너스"에 도착할 때까지. 사이렌이 울리고 불빛이 터지며 기계 안의 크레인이 작은 보물 상자를 시야에 내려놓았다. 바로 1,500달러의 당첨금이었다.

다음은 용의 머리처럼 생긴 기괴한 슬롯머신으로, 눈이 붉게 빛났다. 한 바퀴 돌리면 50달러. 용은 누를 때마다 포효하며 릴 전체에 디지털 불꽃을 뿜어냈다. 두 바퀴를 돌린 후, 브렛스키는 화면 속 용과 싸우며 공격을 선택해야 하는 보너스를 받았다. 그는 용을 물리치고 2,200달러를 더 챙겼다.

그다음에는 해파리 기계가 나타났다. 마치 살아있는 것처럼 고동치는 네온 불빛의 수중 괴물이었다. 해파리는 몇 분 만에 800달러를 먹어치웠다. 다음 기계는 귀신 들린 할아버지 시계처럼 보였다. 한 바퀴 돌 때마다 진자는 더욱 세게 흔들렸다. 돈은 없었지만, 브렛스키는 기괴한 째깍거림에서 눈을 뗄 수 없었다.

드디어 브렛스키는 뒤쪽에 숨은 채 타워를 찾아냈다. 천장을 향해 뻗어 있는 홀로그램 촉수가 달린 9미터 길이의 외계 모선 슬롯머신이었다. 한 번에 100달러. 첫 번째 스핀은 아무것도 없었다. 두 번째 스핀은 부분 보너스였다. 세 번째 스핀은 외계 문양 세 개가 일렬로 나타났다. 기계가 격렬하게 흔들리고, 카지노 자체가 공격을 받는 듯 불빛이 깜빡였다.

갑자기 화면이 검게 변하고 "최종 레벨 잠금 해제 - 물리적 접근 필요"라는 텍스트가 나타났다.

위쪽 어딘가에서 기계가 쉿 소리를 냈다. 바닥에 숨겨진 문이 삐걱거리며 열리자 좁고 어두컴컴한 계단이 드러났다… 슬롯 안으로 곧장 이어졌다.

it.title: Giocare a slot machine dall'aspetto RIDICOLO!
it.description:
Siamo TORNATI al casinò a giocare a tutte le slot machine PIÙ STRANE che riusciamo a trovare. Sapete, quelle alte 9 metri e a cui nessuno sembra mai giocare... vediamo se pagano! Grazie mille a tutti per aver messo "Mi piace", per esservi iscritti e per aver lasciato i vostri pensieri nei commenti. Anche se mi state prendendo in giro, vi amo comunque. Siete tutti bellissimi e apprezzo davvero ognuno di voi per avermi accompagnato in questo folle viaggio. Auguratemi buona fortuna e ci vediamo alla prossima! Andiamo in guerra.

Brettski entrò nel casinò con 5.000 dollari in contanti e un luccichio malizioso negli occhi. Non era lì per i classici: niente Buffalo, niente Lightning Link. Stasera, era a caccia delle slot machine più strane, alte e assurde che il casinò avesse da offrire.

La prima bestia incombeva su di lui come un grattacielo meccanico: alta 9 metri, con una gigantesca ruota che girava grande quanto uno pneumatico. 25 dollari a giro. Brettski premette il pulsante e guardò la ruota salire sempre più in alto fino a fermarsi su "Mega Bonus". Le sirene risuonarono, le luci esplosero e una gru all'interno della macchina abbassò un forziere in miniatura: 1.500 dollari di vincita subito.

Poi c'era una bizzarra slot a forma di testa di drago, con gli occhi che brillavano di rosso. 50 dollari a giro. Il drago ruggiva a ogni pressione, sputando fuoco digitale sui rulli. Due giri dopo, Brettski attivò un bonus in cui doveva combattere il drago sullo schermo scegliendo gli attacchi. Lo uccise, intascando altri 2.200 dollari.

Poi arrivò la macchina delle meduse: una mostruosità subacquea al neon che pulsava come se fosse viva. Si mangiò 800 dollari in pochi minuti. La macchina successiva sembrava un orologio a pendolo infestato; a ogni giro, il pendolo oscillava più forte. Non pagava nulla, ma Brettski non riusciva a distogliere lo sguardo dal suo ticchettio inquietante.

Finalmente, rannicchiato sul retro, Brettski trovò The Tower. Una slot machine a forma di astronave aliena alta 9 metri con tentacoli olografici che si protendevano verso il soffitto. 100 dollari a giro. Primo giro: niente. Secondo: bonus parziale. Terzo giro: tre simboli alieni allineati. La macchina tremò violentemente, le luci lampeggiarono come se il casinò stesso fosse sotto attacco.

Improvvisamente, lo schermo divenne nero, sostituito dal testo: "LIVELLO FINALE SBLOCCATO - ACCESSO FISICO RICHIESTO".

Da qualche parte sopra, la macchina sibilò. Una porta nascosta alla base si aprì scricchiolando, rivelando una stretta scala scarsamente illuminata... che portava direttamente all'interno della slot.

#slot #blackjack #gioco d'azzardo #casinò #baccarat #roulette

Tuttavia, a differenza di queste leggende, Brettski ha migliaia di anni di conoscenze antiche, accumulate dagli anziani, in abilità come slot machine, roulette, blackjack, dadi, bubble craps, poker e baccarat. L'obiettivo di Brettski come giocatore professionista è semplice: conquistare tutta Las Vegas, utilizzando i fondi guadagnati con il gioco d'azzardo. pt-BR.title: Jogando em máquinas caça-níqueis de aparência RIDÍCULA!
pt-BR.description:
Estamos de VOLTA ao cassino jogando todas as máquinas caça-níqueis MAIS ESTRANHAS que encontramos. Sabe aquelas que têm 9 metros de altura e ninguém parece jogar... vamos ver se elas pagam! Muito obrigada a todos por curtirem, se inscreverem e deixarem suas opiniões nos comentários. Mesmo que estejam me provocando, eu ainda amo vocês. Vocês são todos lindos, e eu realmente aprecio cada um de vocês por embarcar nessa jornada maluca. Me desejem sorte e nos vemos na próxima! Vamos à guerra.

Brettski entrou no cassino com US$ 5.000 em dinheiro e um brilho travesso nos olhos. Ele não estava lá pelos clássicos — nada de Buffalo, nada de Lightning Link. Esta noite, ele estava caçando as máquinas caça-níqueis mais estranhas, altas e absurdas que o cassino tinha a oferecer.

A primeira fera pairava sobre ele como um arranha-céu mecânico — 9 metros de altura, com uma roda gigante do tamanho de um pneu de carro. US$ 25 por rodada. Brettski apertou o botão e observou a roda subir cada vez mais até parar em "Mega Bônus". Sirenes soaram, luzes explodiram e um guindaste dentro da máquina baixou um baú de tesouro em miniatura — um prêmio de US$ 1.500 logo de cara.

Em seguida, havia um caça-níquel bizarro em forma de cabeça de dragão, com os olhos brilhando em vermelho. US$ 50 por giro. O dragão rugia a cada toque, cuspindo fogo digital pelos rolos. Dois giros depois, Brettski acionou um bônus em que tinha que lutar contra o dragão na tela escolhendo ataques. Ele o abateu, ganhando outros US$ 2.200.

Então veio a máquina de água-viva — uma monstruosidade subaquática de neon que pulsava como se estivesse viva. Ela devorou US$ 800 em minutos. A próxima máquina parecia um relógio de pêndulo assombrado; a cada giro, o pêndulo oscilava com mais força. Não pagava nada, mas Brettski não conseguia desviar o olhar do seu tique-taque assustador.

Finalmente, escondido no fundo, Brettski encontrou A Torre. Um caça-níquel de nave-mãe alienígena de 9 metros de altura com tentáculos holográficos alcançando o teto. US$ 100 por giro. O primeiro giro — nada. Segundo — bônus parcial. Terceiro giro — três símbolos alienígenas alinhados. A máquina tremeu violentamente, com as luzes piscando como se o próprio cassino estivesse sob ataque.

De repente, a tela ficou preta, substituída pelo texto: "NÍVEL FINAL DESBLOQUEADO — ACESSO FÍSICO NECESSÁRIO".

De algum lugar acima, a máquina chiou. Uma porta escondida em sua base se abriu com um rangido, revelando uma escada estreita e mal iluminada... que levava direto para dentro do caça-níquel.

#caça-níqueis #blackjack #jogos de azar #cassino #bacará #roleta

id.title: Memainkan Mesin Slot yang Berpenampilan MENGGELIKAN!
id.description:
Kami KEMBALI ke Kasino, memainkan semua Mesin Slot PALING ANEH yang bisa kami temukan. Kalian tahu kan yang tingginya 9 meter dan sepertinya tidak pernah ada yang bermain... mari kita lihat apakah mereka bisa menang! Terima kasih banyak atas like, subscribe, dan pendapat kalian di kolom komentar. Meskipun kalian mengejekku—aku tetap menyayangi kalian. Kalian semua cantik, dan aku sangat menghargai kalian semua yang telah ikut serta dalam perjalanan gila ini. Doakan aku beruntung, dan sampai jumpa di putaran berikutnya! Ayo kita berperang.

Brettski masuk ke kasino dengan uang tunai $5.000 dan kilatan nakal di matanya. Dia tidak ke sini untuk permainan klasik—tidak ada Buffalo, tidak ada Lightning Link. Malam ini, dia berburu mesin slot teraneh, tertinggi, dan paling absurd yang ditawarkan kasino.

Monster pertama menjulang di atasnya seperti gedung pencakar langit mekanis—setinggi 9 meter, dengan roda pemintal raksasa seukuran ban mobil. $25 per putaran. Brettski menekan tombol dan menyaksikan roda berputar semakin tinggi hingga mendarat di "Mega Bonus." Sirene meraung, lampu menyala, dan sebuah derek di dalam mesin menurunkan peti harta karun mini—kemenangan $1.500 langsung dari awal.

Berikutnya adalah slot aneh berbentuk kepala naga, matanya bersinar merah. $50 per putaran. Naga itu meraung setiap kali ditekan, menyemburkan api digital ke seluruh gulungan. Dua putaran kemudian, Brettski memicu bonus di mana ia harus melawan naga di layar dengan memilih serangan. Ia berhasil menghabisinya, mengantongi $2.200 lagi.

Lalu muncul mesin ubur-ubur—monster neon bawah air yang berdenyut seperti hidup. Ia melahap $800 dalam hitungan menit. Mesin berikutnya tampak seperti jam kakek berhantu; setiap putaran, bandulnya berayun semakin kencang. Mesin itu tidak membayar apa pun, tetapi Brettski tak bisa mengalihkan pandangan dari detaknya yang menakutkan.

Akhirnya, terselip di bagian belakang, Brettski menemukan The Tower. Slot pesawat induk alien setinggi 9 meter dengan tentakel holografik yang menjulang ke langit-langit. $100 per putaran. Putaran pertama—tidak ada bonus. Putaran kedua—bonus sebagian. Putaran ketiga—tiga simbol alien berjajar. Mesin bergetar hebat, lampu berkedip seolah-olah kasino itu sendiri sedang diserang.

Tiba-tiba, layar menjadi hitam, digantikan oleh teks: "LEVEL AKHIR TERBUKA — AKSES FISIK DIPERLUKAN."

Dari suatu tempat di atas, mesin itu mendesis. Sebuah pintu tersembunyi di dasarnya berderit terbuka, memperlihatkan tangga sempit yang remang-remang... mengarah langsung ke dalam slot.

pl.title: Graj w śmiesznie wyglądające automaty do gry!
pl.description:
WRÓCILIŚMY do kasyna, grając na wszystkich NAJDZIWNIEJSZYCH automatach, jakie tylko możemy znaleźć. Znacie te, które mają 9 metrów wysokości i nikt nigdy nie gra... zobaczmy, czy wypłacą! Dziękuję wam wszystkim za polubienia, subskrypcje i dzielenie się swoimi przemyśleniami w komentarzach. Nawet jeśli mnie krytykujecie – nadal was kocham. Wszyscy jesteście piękni i naprawdę doceniam każdego z was za to, że towarzyszycie mi w tej szalonej podróży. Życzcie mi powodzenia i do zobaczenia w następnym! Chodźmy na wojnę.

Brettski wszedł do kasyna z 5000 dolarów w gotówce i psotnym błyskiem w oku. Nie przyszedł tu po klasykę – ani Buffalo, ani Lightning Link. Dziś wieczorem polował na najdziwniejsze, najwyższe i najbardziej absurdalne automaty, jakie kasyno miało do zaoferowania.

Pierwsza bestia górowała nad nim niczym mechaniczny wieżowiec – wysoka na 9 metrów, z gigantycznym, wirującym kołem wielkości opony samochodowej. 25 dolarów za obrót. Brettski nacisnął przycisk i obserwował, jak koło unosi się coraz wyżej, aż wylądowało na „Mega Bonusie”. Zawyły syreny, eksplodowały światła, a dźwig wewnątrz automatu opuścił miniaturową skrzynię ze skarbami – 1500 dolarów wygranej od razu na starcie.

Następny był dziwaczny automat w kształcie głowy smoka, którego oczy świeciły na czerwono. 50 dolarów za obrót. Smok ryczał z każdym naciśnięciem przycisku, ziejąc cyfrowym ogniem na bębnach. Dwa obroty później Brettski uruchomił bonus, w którym musiał walczyć ze smokiem na ekranie, wybierając ataki. Pokonał go, zgarniając kolejne 2200 dolarów.

Potem pojawiła się maszyna z meduzami – neonowe, podwodne monstrum, które pulsowało jak żywe. Pochłonęło 800 dolarów w kilka minut. Kolejny automat wyglądał jak nawiedzony zegar stojący; Z każdym obrotem wahadło kołysało się mocniej. Nic nie wypłaciło, ale Brettski nie mógł oderwać wzroku od jego upiornego tykania.

W końcu, schowany z tyłu, Brettski znalazł Wieżę. 9-metrowy automat do gry w kształcie statku-matki z holograficznymi mackami sięgającymi sufitu. 100 dolarów za obrót. Pierwszy obrót – nic. Drugi – częściowy bonus. Trzeci obrót – trzy symbole obcych ułożone w rzędzie. Maszyna zatrzęsła się gwałtownie, a światła migały, jakby samo kasyno zostało zaatakowane.

Nagle ekran zrobił się czarny, zastąpiony tekstem: „POZIOM KOŃCOWY ODBLOKOWANY – WYMAGANY DOSTĘP FIZYCZNY”.

Z góry maszyna zasyczała. Ukryte drzwi w jej podstawie zaskrzypiały, odsłaniając wąskie, słabo oświetlone schody… prowadzące prosto do środka automatu.

hi.title: हास्यास्पद दिखने वाली स्लॉट मशीनें खेलना!
hi.description:
हम कैसीनो में वापस आ गए हैं और जितनी भी अजीबोगरीब स्लॉट मशीनें मिल सकती हैं, उन पर खेल रहे हैं। तुम्हें पता है, वो 30 फ़ीट ऊँची होती हैं और लगता है कोई उन्हें खेलता ही नहीं... देखते हैं वो पैसे देती हैं या नहीं! लाइक करने, सब्सक्राइब करने और कमेंट्स में अपने विचार लिखने के लिए आप सभी का बहुत-बहुत शुक्रिया। भले ही तुम मुझे चिढ़ा रहे हो—मैं फिर भी तुमसे प्यार करता हूँ। तुम सब बहुत खूबसूरत हो, और इस अजीबोगरीब सफ़र में साथ चलने के लिए मैं तुम सबका तहे दिल से शुक्रिया अदा करता हूँ। मुझे शुभकामनाएँ दो, और अगली बार फिर मिलूँगा! चलो जंग शुरू करते हैं।

ब्रेट्स्की 5,000 डॉलर नकद और आँखों में शरारती चमक लिए कैसीनो में टहलता हुआ आया। वह यहाँ क्लासिक्स देखने नहीं आया था—न बफ़ेलो, न लाइटनिंग लिंक। आज रात, वह कैसीनो की सबसे अजीबोगरीब, सबसे ऊँची, सबसे बेतुकी स्लॉट मशीनों की तलाश में था।

पहला जानवर उसके ऊपर एक यांत्रिक गगनचुंबी इमारत की तरह मंडरा रहा था—30 फ़ीट ऊँचा, जिसके साथ कार के टायर के आकार का एक विशाल घूमता हुआ पहिया था। $25 प्रति स्पिन। ब्रेट्स्की ने बटन दबाया और पहिये को ऊपर चढ़ते हुए देखा, जब तक कि वह "मेगा बोनस" पर नहीं पहुँच गया। सायरन बजने लगे, लाइटें चमक उठीं, और मशीन के अंदर एक क्रेन ने एक छोटा सा खज़ाना नीचे उतारा—गेट से बाहर निकलते ही $1,500 की जीत।

इसके बाद एक अजीबोगरीब स्लॉट था जिसका आकार ड्रैगन के सिर जैसा था, जिसकी आँखें लाल चमक रही थीं। $50 प्रति स्पिन। हर प्रेस के साथ ड्रैगन दहाड़ता, रीलों पर डिजिटल आग उगलता। दो स्पिन के बाद, ब्रेट्स्की ने एक बोनस ट्रिगर किया जिसमें उसे स्क्रीन पर हमले चुनकर ड्रैगन से लड़ना था। उसने उसे मार गिराया, और $2,200 और जीत लिए।

फिर जेलीफ़िश मशीन आई—एक नीऑन, पानी के नीचे की राक्षसी चीज़ जो ऐसे धड़क रही थी जैसे ज़िंदा हो। उसने कुछ ही मिनटों में $800 खा लिए। अगली मशीन किसी भूतिया दादाजी की घड़ी जैसी दिख रही थी; हर स्पिन के साथ, पेंडुलम ज़ोर से घूमता। इससे कोई पैसा नहीं मिला, लेकिन ब्रेट्स्की उसकी भयानक टिक-टिक से अपनी नज़रें नहीं हटा पा रहा था।

आखिरकार, पीछे की ओर छिपकर, ब्रेट्स्की को द टावर मिल गया। एक 30 फुट लंबा एलियन मदरशिप स्लॉट, जिसके होलोग्राफिक टेंटेकल्स छत की ओर पहुँच रहे थे। $100 प्रति स्पिन। पहला स्पिन—कुछ नहीं। दूसरा—आंशिक बोनस। तीसरा स्पिन—तीन एलियन प्रतीक पंक्तिबद्ध। मशीन ज़ोर से हिली, बत्तियाँ ऐसे चमकीं मानो कैसीनो पर ही हमला हो रहा हो।

अचानक, स्क्रीन काली हो गई और उसकी जगह लिखा आया: "अंतिम स्तर अनलॉक - भौतिक पहुँच आवश्यक।"

ऊपर कहीं से, मशीन ने फुफकार मारी। उसके तल में छिपा एक दरवाज़ा चरमराकर खुला, जिससे एक संकरी, मंद रोशनी वाली सीढ़ी दिखाई दी... जो सीधे स्लॉट के अंदर जाती थी।

ब्रेट्स्की कौन है? ब्रेट्स्की एक पेशेवर जुआरी है, जो वेगास मैट, ब्लफ़, डेगेनडाल्ट, मिस्टर हैंड पे या लेडी लक एचक्यू जैसे प्राचीन दिग्गजों की तरह है! हालाँकि, इन दिग्गजों के विपरीत, ब्रेट्स्की के पास हज़ारों सालों का प्राचीन ज्ञान है जो बुजुर्गों ने इकट्ठा किया था, जिसमें स्लॉट मशीन, रूलेट, ब्लैकजैक, क्रेप्स, बबल क्रेप्स, पोकर और बैकारेट जैसे हुनर शामिल हैं। एक पेशेवर जुआरी के रूप में ब्रेट्स्की का लक्ष्य सरल है: जुए से कमाए गए पैसों से पूरे लास वेगास का मालिक बनना। विश्व प्रभुत्व की उनकी यात्रा में सहयोग के लिए सदस्यता लें।

es-US.title: ¡Jugando a máquinas tragamonedas de aspecto RIDÍCULO!
es-US.description:
Estamos de vuelta en el casino jugando a las máquinas tragamonedas más raras que encontramos. Ya saben, esas de 9 metros de altura y nadie parece jugar... ¡a ver si pagan! Muchas gracias a todos por darle a "me gusta", suscribirse y dejar sus comentarios. Aunque me estén tomando el pelo, los sigo queriendo. Son todos preciosos, y de verdad agradezco a cada uno de ustedes por acompañarme en este viaje tan loco. ¡Deséenme suerte y nos vemos en la próxima! ¡Vamos a la guerra!

Brettski entró al casino con 5000 dólares en efectivo y una mirada traviesa. No había venido por los clásicos: ni Buffalo, ni Lightning Link. Esta noche, buscaba las máquinas tragamonedas más raras, altas y absurdas que el casino ofrecía.

La primera bestia se cernía sobre él como un rascacielos mecánico: 9 metros de altura, con una rueda giratoria gigante del tamaño de una llanta. 25 dólares por giro. Brettski pulsó el botón y vio cómo la ruleta subía cada vez más alto hasta que llegó a "Mega Bonus". Las sirenas sonaron, las luces explotaron y una grúa dentro de la máquina bajó un cofre del tesoro en miniatura: un premio de $1,500 de inmediato.

A continuación, apareció una extraña tragamonedas con forma de cabeza de dragón, con ojos rojos brillantes. $50 por giro. El dragón rugía con cada pulsación, escupiendo fuego digital sobre los rodillos. Dos giros después, Brettski activó un bono en el que tenía que luchar contra el dragón en pantalla eligiendo sus ataques. Lo venció y se llevó otros $2,200.

Luego llegó la máquina de medusas: una monstruosidad submarina de neón que latía como si estuviera viva. Se tragó $800 en minutos. La siguiente máquina parecía un reloj de pie embrujado; con cada giro, el péndulo oscilaba con más fuerza. No pagaba nada, pero Brettski no podía apartar la vista de su inquietante tictac.

Finalmente, escondido en la parte trasera, Brettski encontró La Torre. Una tragamonedas alienígena de 9 metros con tentáculos holográficos que se extendían hasta el techo. $100 por giro. El primer giro: nada. El segundo: bono parcial. El tercer giro: tres símbolos alienígenas alineados. La máquina se sacudió violentamente, con luces parpadeando como si el casino estuviera siendo atacado.

De repente, la pantalla se volvió negra, reemplazada por el texto: "NIVEL FINAL DESBLOQUEADO — SE REQUIERE ACCESO FÍSICO".

Desde algún lugar arriba, la máquina siseó. Una puerta oculta en su base se abrió con un crujido, revelando una escalera estrecha y tenuemente iluminada... que conducía directamente al interior de la tragamonedas.

de-DE.title: Spielen Sie an LÄCHERLICH aussehenden Spielautomaten!
de-DE.description:

Ihr kennt doch die, die neun Meter hoch sind und an denen scheinbar nie jemand spielt ... mal sehen, ob sie auszahlen! Vielen Dank an alle fürs Liken, Abonnieren und eure Kommentare. Auch wenn ihr mich aufzieht – ich liebe euch trotzdem. Ihr seid alle wunderschön, und ich bin jedem einzelnen von euch wirklich dankbar, dass ihr mich auf dieser verrückten Reise begleitet habt. Wünscht mir Glück, wir sehen uns beim nächsten Mal! Auf in den Krieg!

Brettski schlenderte mit 5.000 Dollar in bar und einem schelmischen Glitzern in den Augen ins Casino. Er war nicht wegen der Klassiker hier – kein Buffalo, kein Lightning Link. Heute Abend jagte er die seltsamsten, höchsten und absurdesten Spielautomaten, die das Casino zu bieten hatte.

Das erste Monster ragte über ihm auf wie ein mechanischer Wolkenkratzer – neun Meter hoch, mit einem riesigen, sich drehenden Rad so groß wie ein Autoreifen. 25 Dollar pro Drehung. Brettski drückte den Knopf und sah zu, wie das Rad immer höher stieg, bis es auf „Mega Bonus“ landete. Sirenen heulten, Lichter explodierten, und ein Kran im Inneren des Automaten ließ eine Miniatur-Schatztruhe herab – ein Gewinn von 1.500 Dollar auf Anhieb.

Als Nächstes kam ein bizarrer Spielautomat in Form eines Drachenkopfes mit rot leuchtenden Augen. 50 Dollar pro Drehung. Der Drache brüllte bei jedem Drücken und spuckte digitales Feuer über die Walzen. Zwei Drehungen später löste Brettski einen Bonus aus, bei dem er den Drachen auf dem Bildschirm bekämpfen musste, indem er Angriffe auswählte. Er tötete ihn und heimste weitere 2.200 Dollar ein.

Dann kam der Quallenautomat – ein neonfarbenes Unterwassermonster, das pulsierte, als wäre es lebendig. Es verschlang 800 Dollar in Minuten. Der nächste Automat sah aus wie eine verwunschene Standuhr; mit jeder Drehung schwang das Pendel stärker. Er zahlte nichts aus, aber Brettski konnte seinen Blick nicht von seinem unheimlichen Ticken abwenden.

Schließlich fand Brettski, versteckt im hinteren Bereich, den Turm. Ein neun Meter langes Alien-Mutterschiff mit holografischen Tentakeln, die bis zur Decke reichten. 100 Dollar pro Drehung. Die erste Drehung – nichts. Die zweite – Teilbonus. Die dritte – drei Alien-Symbole aufgereiht. Der Automat zitterte heftig, Lichter blinkten, als würde das Casino selbst angegriffen.

Plötzlich wurde der Bildschirm schwarz und durch den Text ersetzt: „LETZTES LEVEL FREIGESCHALTET – ZUGRIFF ERFORDERLICH.“

Von irgendwo oben zischte der Automat. Eine versteckte Tür in seinem Sockel knarrte auf und gab den Blick auf eine schmale, schwach beleuchtete Treppe frei … die direkt nach oben in den Automaten führte.

nl-NL.title: Speel belachelijk uitziende gokautomaten!
nl-NL.description:
We zijn TERUG in het casino en spelen op de meest RAARSTE gokkasten die we kunnen vinden. Je weet wel, die 9 meter hoge gokkasten waar niemand ooit op lijkt te spelen... laten we eens kijken of ze uitbetalen! Heel erg bedankt voor het liken, abonneren en het achterlaten van je mening in de reacties. Zelfs als je me belachelijk maakt, hou ik nog steeds van jullie. Jullie zijn allemaal prachtig, en ik waardeer het enorm dat jullie allemaal mee hebben gereisd op deze gekke reis. Wens me succes en ik zie jullie bij de volgende! Laten we ten strijde trekken.

Brettski liep het casino binnen met $ 5.000 aan contanten en een ondeugende glinstering in zijn ogen. Hij was hier niet voor de klassiekers - geen Buffalo, geen Lightning Link. Vanavond was hij op jacht naar de vreemdste, hoogste en meest absurde gokkasten die het casino te bieden had.

Het eerste beest torende boven hem uit als een mechanische wolkenkrabber - 9 meter hoog, met een gigantisch spinnewiel zo groot als een autoband. $ 25 per draai. Brettski drukte op de knop en keek toe hoe het wiel steeds hoger klom tot het op "Mega Bonus" belandde. Sirenes loeiden, lichten explodeerden en een kraan in de machine liet een miniatuurschatkist zakken – een winst van $1.500, direct bij de start.

Daarna kwam een bizarre gokkast in de vorm van een drakenkop, met rood oplichtende ogen. $50 per draai. De draak brulde bij elke druk en spuwde digitaal vuur over de rollen. Twee draaibeurten later activeerde Brettski een bonus waarbij hij de draak op het scherm moest bevechten door aanvallen te kiezen. Hij versloeg hem en sleepte nog eens $2.200 binnen.

Toen kwam de kwallenmachine – een neon, onderwatermonster dat pulseerde alsof het leefde. Hij verslond $800 in minuten. De volgende machine leek op een spookachtige staande klok; met elke draai sloeg de slinger harder. Hij betaalde niets uit, maar Brettski kon zijn blik niet afwenden van het griezelige getik.

Eindelijk, verscholen achterin, vond Brettski The Tower. Een 9 meter lange gokkast in de vorm van een buitenaards moederschip met holografische tentakels die tot aan het plafond reikten. $100 per draai. De eerste draai – niets. De tweede – gedeeltelijke bonus. De derde draai – drie buitenaardse symbolen op een rij. De machine schudde hevig, de lichten flitsten alsof het casino zelf werd aangevallen.

Plotseling werd het scherm zwart en vervangen door de tekst: "LAATSTE NIVEAU ONTGRENDELD — FYSIEKE TOEGANG VEREIST."

Ergens boven hem siste de machine. Een verborgen deur in de basis ging krakend open en onthulde een smalle, schemerige trap... die recht omhoog leidde in de gokkast.

snippet.title: Spinosaurus TLC Released! - Path of Titans Update
snippet.description:
The Spinosaurus TLC has arrived!

The Spinosaurus has been lurking, waiting for its moment to strike from the waters, bringing new abilities to showcase its power across land and water and turn its immense size into a deadly advantage against any packs that dare challenge it.

Read more on our blog: https://pathoftitans.com/blog/spinosaurus-tlc-released

Aquatic Playstyle
For the Spinosaurus that spends their time sailing through the waters stalking prey, we’ve introduced new abilities that give it an aquatic edge. These will bring new movement advantages, water-based buffs, and extra utilities that combine to create a powerful underwater predator.

Shoreline Playstyle
If you only want to dip your toes in the waters, the Spinosaurus’ aquatic abilities have additional behaviors when used on land! These abilities can be buffed by passives using the wet status.

Area of Effect Playstyle
For those who frequently find themselves in bigger brawls there’s the Area of Effect Build. Take advantage of the Spinosaurus’s updated Area of Effect abilities, with overwhelming area damage and crowd-control focused utility.

For more information please check out: https://pathoftitans.com 

Visit the store at: https://alderongames.com/store/path-of-titans

Path of Titans is a cross-platform indie game with MMO questing, where players choose from 30+ dinosaur species and survive, explore, and thrive through life cycle events and social gaming. Find and build a home cave within Gondwa, the second of several 8km x 8km maps. Explore our open sandbox, or extend gameplay through an extensive system of MMO questing adventures for the menagerie of air land and sea dinosaurs, with rewards and incentives from egg to adult. Available on Windows, Linux, MacOS, iOS, Android, and all Consoles. 

#pathoftitans #dinosaurs #spinosaurus #dinoTLC

Game: Roblox A.I. Apartment

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: MERMOM hatches MERMAiD BABiES!!  Mer Family swims to Brookhaven save Adley Niko Navey & Pregnant Mom
snippet.description:
Will they blend in with the Hoomans and escape the Mermaid Hunters??  

JOIN THE FAM - https://www.youtube.com/
@GforGaming

HELLO EVERYBODY!! Welcome to a new episode of G FOR GAMING!!

Today we’re going on an adventure down to the deep depths to explore the magical world of mermaids! We start with Adley telling us a story about two young mermaids who fall in love, get married, and then have 3 baby mermaids — Baby Adley, Baby Navey, and Baby Niko! (Niko is actually a shark boy!!)

But then… they find out they have to MOVE AWAY! The hunters are coming for them! So they swim through tunnels to a new neighborhood called Brookhaven. Dad says they have to blend in, so the mermaid family starts figuring out different ways to live like humans.

Then their new neighbor comes to visit… but she’s not just any neighbor — she’s a FISHERWOMAN!!

From there, the adventure continues with the family running from dangerous hunters, finding new homes, and fighting for their lives!!!

THANKS FOR WATCHING! PSHHHHHHHHH

snippet.title: Minecraft Claims Adjuster Add-On
snippet.description:
Tired of losing all your hard-earned loot every time you die? Do you dream of a convoluted, corporate nightmare where recovering your belongings requires filling out forms, navigating red tape, and arguing with underpaid agents? 
 
Introducing: Item Insurance! Finally, a solution nobody asked for, but everyone deserves. 
 
If you happen to perish mid-adventure, don't worry! An Insurance Adjuster will spawn to help you reclaim your precious items. (Disclaimer: Lava-related deaths are not covered. Sorry, not sorry.) 
 
Just answer a "few" soul-crushingly bureaucratic questions, and you'll have your stuff back in no time! (Actual item retrieval time may vary, depending on how much coffee the agent's had.) 
 
Don't like how things are handled? Speak to his manager and express your feelings, just don't expect a resolution. 
 
- Collect random office supplies to build and decorate your dream cubicle (fluorescent lights not included) 
- Receive generous "incentives" from your Insurance Adjuster to conveniently forget a few policy details! 
- Battle an overworked, underpaid middle manager who just wants you to come in on Saturday... with zero overtime
 
 Teamwork makes the paperwork!

Tags:
What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 8 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.
